We stored 123 at [sp+0]:
    str  x1, [sp]          // stores at sp+0

So we must load it from the same address:
    ldr  x0, [sp]          // loads from sp+0 = 123  ✓
    ldr  x0, [sp, #8]      // loads from sp+8 = garbage  ✗

The offset in the LDR must match the offset used in the STR.

Stack visualization:
    [sp+0]  = 123   ← stored here
    [sp+8]  = ???   ← never written, could be anything
